OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774832614
OL,3,CHousing market 'increasingly relying
OL,4,Con a smaller pool of serious buyers'
OL,6,FHome buyer demand weakened in March as
OL,7,Frising mortgage rates and global
OL,8,Funcertainty linked to the Middle East
OL,9,Fconflict dampened confidence,
OL,10,Faccording to a property website.
OL,12,FZoopla said that agreed sales have
OL,13,Ffallen by 2% annually, with the market
OL,14,Fbeing supported by committed movers
OL,15,Fwho already have mortgages agreed.
OL,17,FBut sales agreed are flat or slightly
OL,18,Fhigher in some parts of the UK, such
OL,19,Fas Wales, Yorkshire and the Humber and
OL,20,FLondon, compared with last year, it
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
