CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774832614
OL,3,CHousing market 'increasingly relying
OL,4,Con a smaller pool of serious buyers'
OL,6,FBuyer inquiries were 13% lower than a
OL,7,Fyear ago as potential buyers adopt a
OL,8,Fmore cautious, "wait and see"
OL,9,Fapproach, Zoopla's report said.
OL,11,FIt said that buyer demand has been
OL,12,Frunning below last year's levels
OL,13,Facross the first three months of the
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe overall number of homes for sale
OL,17,Fhas increased by 6% annually,
OL,18,Freflecting a continued desire among
OL,19,Fhomeowners to move despite the more
OL,20,Funcertain backdrop.
