CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774832614
OL,3,CHousing market 'increasingly relying
OL,4,Con a smaller pool of serious buyers'
OL,6,FZoopla said a significant proportion
OL,7,Fof transactions are also less
OL,8,Fsensitive to rising mortgage rates.
OL,10,FAround a quarter of sales are cash
OL,11,Fpurchases, while many existing
OL,12,Fhomeowners have built up equity and
OL,13,Fsecured borrowing in advance, reducing
OL,14,Fthe impact of higher mortgage rates.
OL,16,FThis is helping to support sales in
OL,17,Fthe short term, but also highlights
OL,18,Fgrowing reliance on less mortgage rate-
OL,19,Fsensitive home buyers, the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
