OL,3,CHousing market 'increasingly relying
OL,4,Con a smaller pool of serious buyers'
OL,6,FOverall, UK house price inflation is
OL,7,Fholding steady, with 1.3% annual
OL,8,Fgrowth.
OL,10,FPrice growth is strongest in more
OL,11,Faffordable areas, with the north west
OL,12,Fof England recording an annual
OL,13,Fincrease of 3.5%, Zoopla said.
OL,15,FLenders have been scrambling to hike
OL,16,Fmortgage rates and withdraw some
OL,17,Fproducts amid changing expectations in
OL,18,Fthe financial markets.
OL,20,FSwap rates, which are used by lenders
OL,21,Fto price mortgages, have been rising.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
