CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774832614
OL,3,CHousing market 'increasingly relying
OL,4,Con a smaller pool of serious buyers'
OL,6,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,7,FZoopla, said: "The market remains
OL,8,Factive, but becoming increasingly
OL,9,Freliant on a smaller pool of serious
OL,10,Fbuyers.
OL,12,F"Some early stage buyers are adopting
OL,13,Fa wait and see approach but there is a
OL,14,Fsizable group of committed buyers who
OL,15,Fare pressing ahead with housing
OL,16,Fpurchases."
OL,18,FZoopla's house price index measures
OL,19,Fthe change in house prices where sales
OL,20,Fare agreed.
