OL,3,CHousing market 'increasingly relying
OL,4,Con a smaller pool of serious buyers'
OL,6,FData on sales agreed and buyer demand
OL,7,Fcovers the four weeks to March 22
OL,8,Fcompared with a year earlier. Its
OL,9,Fhouse price figures cover the period
OL,10,Fup to the end of February.
OL,12,FHere are annual house price changes,
OL,13,Faccording to Zoopla:
OL,15,FLondon, minus 0.2%
OL,17,FSouth East, minus 0.2%
OL,19,FSouth West, 0.0%
OL,21,FEastern England, 0.6%
